 &quot;Look here folks, we've got international cooperation in a new venture into a literally limitless frontier. It offers unlimited advancement for every human alive and all of our descendants.<br>
It's a nice synergy that in this venture, we're using the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> exact same technology which makes horrible weapons of mass destruction</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> in a hopeful venture. Arguably, nothing else we have available does job as well.<br>
